channel.title: RsSkills - ReRelease. [Pi]
channel.description:
Ok, So i woke up this morning to find my vps HACKED along with my webserver. and i nice little note telling me who'd done it. So after speaking to her for a while, i decided there is no point in continuing to run the server and remake like 4 weeks of updates. So i am re releasing the only backup i have. I released this about 2 months ago but then removed it for multiple reasons. So i am now re-releasing for you guys to enjoy. [center][b]DO NOT PM ME ASKING FOR HELP WITH THIS[/b][/center] [b]Features[/b]
All skills are trainable. Good economy All monsters drop items Many boss monsters Improved combat system Making of all potions Donator & Super donator areas Added features for super donators
Media [center] *Note* This media is from my server which is same base so not much changed. [img]http://screensnapr.com/e/mIlb38.png[/img] [img]http://screensnapr.com/e/FGqDP9.png[/img] [img]http://screensnapr.com/e/G0kI5l.png[/img] Basically all teh stuff that dspk has but improved stability and more things to make more fun gameplatt [/center] The server has a shutdown hook intergrated with extra security for x logging and such Every skill is trainable and have average xp rates for a good speed training. The slowest skills are fishing and runecrafting. every monster drops something. Download Package- uppit: [url=http://uppit.com/cdi6wsoblcfa/Package.zip]http://uppit.com/cdi6wsoblcfa/Package.zip [/url] Package- Mirror 1: Being Uploaded [b]Commands[/b] [code]Normal People - ::report playername - ::snowball - teles to icy place for chill Donators - ::Yell Mods - ::Mute - ::unmute - ::ban - ::unban - ::jail - ::unjail Admins - ::ipban - ::ipmute - ::unipmute - ::master - ::pure Owner - ::givedonor - ::givesuper - ::givemod - ::giveadmin - ::giveowner - ::givehidden - ::giveforum - ::setlevel - ::god - ::pnpc - ::npc - ::item - ::gfx[/code]
